Module: Single Notification
Author: Thomas Seifert

This module limits the notifications to one per thread until the forum is visited again.

Installation instructions:
--------------------------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "single_notification" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Single Notification".

